[node name="Viewer" type="RichTextView" parent="VBox/HSplit/ViewerBg" unique_id=1274428550]
markdown_text = "# RichTextView

Read-only display of rich text content.

## Supported elements

1. **Bold** and *italic* text
2. Headings (H1-H6)
3. Ordered and unordered lists
4. Block quotes
5. Horizontal rules

> quote

```
Block code
```

`inline code quote`

---

Click on [links](#) to trigger the `link_clicked` signal."
